title: Ambedo | Ayusy
description:
"The deeper you try to dive into life, the more you spend on the shallows. You just end back on the shore trying to go deeper.
The best you can hope for is to see where the road takes you. To let your mind wander and enjoy the ride. To find those moments when everything falls quite, the words loose their meaning and it all mixes together. Until you cant tell the difference between the oridinary and the epic. And you stop waiting around for some other meaning to arrive you notice how delicate and fleeting it all seems."
